            <title>[FLINK-6899] Wrong state array size in NestedMapsStateTable</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/FLINK-6899</link>
                <project id="12315522" key="FLINK">Flink</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;The &lt;tt&gt;NestedMapsStateTable&lt;/tt&gt; initializes the internal state array with a wrong size which leads to a waste of memory. We should initialize the array with the number of key groups of the assigned range instead of the max parallelism.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
